{{BLP sources|date=February 2010}} {{Infobox comics creator | image
| imagesize = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_place = | death_place = | nationality = American | cartoonist = | write = | art = | pencil = y | ink = y | edit = | publish = | letter = | color = | alias = | notable works = ''[[Freddy vs. Jason vs. Ash]]'', ''[[Evil Ernie]]'' | awards = | website = | subcat = American | birth_date={{Birth date and age|1974|6|26}} }} '''Jason Craig''' (born June 26, 1974, [[Eglin Air Force Base]] in [[Niceville, Florida|Niceville, FL]]) is an [[People of the United States|American]] [[comic book artist]]
==Career== Jason Craig started his career in Chicago, in 1991, working on and off for various publishers before moving away to pursue a full-time career in advertising. Following a near-fatal automobile accident in 2002, Craig was placed into a coma briefly and spent the following year in physical rehab, after which he returned to Chicago to continue his career in comics.{{Citation needed|date=January 2010}}
Craig's most notable work in the comics' industry has been for [[Wildstorm]] Comics, drawing ''[[Freddy vs. Jason vs. Ash]]'' and [[Freddy vs. Jason vs. Ash 2: Nightmare Warriors|its sequel]].<ref name=RetroSlashers>{{cite web |url=http://retroslashers.net/blog/exclusive-interview-with-freddy-vs-jason-vs-ash-2-artist-jason-craig/ |title=Exclusive Interview With Freddy vs. Jason vs. Ash 2 Artist Jason Craig |publisher=RetroSlashers |date=May 24, 2009 |accessdate=September 16, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090628150923/http://retroslashers.net/blog/exclusive-interview-with-freddy-vs-jason-vs-ash-2-artist-jason-craig/ |archivedate=June 28, 2009 |df= }}</ref>
Craig drew the reboot issues of the comic series ''[[Evil Ernie]]'', written by [[Jesse Blaze Snider]]. The first issue was released in October 2012.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/205795/could-it-be-dynamite-to-resurrect-evil-ernie-with-jesse-blaze-snider-and-jason-craig/|title=Could It Be? Dynamite To Resurrect Evil Ernie With Jesse Blaze Snider And Jason Craig - Bloody Disgusting|website=bloody-disgusting.com}}</ref>
